Interface IProtocol

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminProtocol, BoatProtocol, TestProtocol, UserProtocol

    public interface IProtocol
    IProtocol is the interface defining the common behavior the central system can use and the subclasses have to consider

    IProtocol and only has only one method 'execute' to decipher instructions coming from an Automaton
